<p><strong>To enable this feature you can follow these simple steps:</strong></p>

<ol>
  <li>Log into your <strong>Admin Panel</strong></li>
  <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> &gt; <strong>Advertisement</strong> &gt; <strong>Publish Options</strong></li>
  <li>Set <strong>Require login to post</strong> value to <strong>ON</strong></li>
  <li>Press <strong>Save</strong></li>
</ol>

<p>And youâ€™re good to go!</p>

